Actions on Project

To view actions available on the Projects select the Action option. A list with all actions/groups of actions will be displayed.

The actions depend on the Project state. The following Projects states are possible:

  • In Progress - Active state of the Project. All Project actions can be performed - create conservation activity, create document, etc.
  • Completed and Locked - The Project in Completed and Locked state is inactive. Only the permissions of the Project,  Reopen and all print and export actions are visible.
